Name: Grilled Fern Spore
AttributesDescription: Increases Crit. DMG of all Resonators in the team by 32%, lasting for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: Young fern balls are picked, skewered, and grilled—one of the most common Royan greens. They have a noticeable bitterness. Fans say the aftertaste is pleasantly sweet, calling it “the taste of adulthood.” Royan children avoid them, but anyone who can finish a whole skewer without making a face earns bragging rights.
